WEBVTT

00:34.670 --> 00:36.150
It smells so good.

00:36.320 --> 00:37.560
What's cooking?

00:38.640 --> 00:40.240
I'd really like to have some.

00:52.030 --> 00:53.520
My sister is making
a tasty braised dish again.

00:53.520 --> 00:54.320
What is it?

00:54.320 --> 00:55.450
I'm not telling you.

01:05.200 --> 01:05.860
Changning,

01:06.070 --> 01:08.200
tell Mrs. Zhao not to make dinner.

01:08.640 --> 01:11.240
We'll send them noodles
with pork intestines.

01:12.760 --> 01:13.420
Go do it now.

01:26.870 --> 01:28.600
You little glutton. Off you go.

01:32.070 --> 01:33.680
Mrs. Zhao,

01:34.000 --> 01:36.800
my sister says
you don't need to make dinner today,

01:37.039 --> 01:40.560
since she'll cook noodles
with pork intestines for you.

03:07.960 --> 03:13.280
[Pursuit of Jade]

03:13.370 --> 03:15.940
[Episode 2]

03:18.079 --> 03:19.590
Dinner's ready!

03:24.750 --> 03:26.360
Mr. Zhao made you a crutch.

03:28.560 --> 03:29.190
Thanks.

03:45.560 --> 03:47.280
No pig's tail at all.

03:47.710 --> 03:49.310
We're having "meat gourds" today.

03:49.310 --> 03:51.240
I'll braise a pig's tail tomorrow.

03:58.150 --> 03:59.950
Have you forgotten Mom's rules?

04:00.120 --> 04:02.780
Don't be rude.
We can't eat until the guest does.

04:04.910 --> 04:06.710
We'll eat after you, sir.

04:07.430 --> 04:08.110
Thanks.

04:37.800 --> 04:39.680
You've been having porridge these days.

04:39.680 --> 04:41.740
Is one bowl of noodles enough for you?

04:42.920 --> 04:44.450
O-One bowl of noodles is...

04:44.920 --> 04:45.520
enough...

04:45.560 --> 04:46.560
You're in recovery.

04:46.560 --> 04:47.690
You should eat more.

04:48.680 --> 04:49.480
Yes, eat more.

04:54.830 --> 04:55.480
Thank you.

05:03.270 --> 05:03.920
Is it good?

05:06.040 --> 05:06.900
Yes, very good.

05:08.270 --> 05:09.560
What exactly...

05:09.630 --> 05:10.690
are "meat gourds"?

05:11.040 --> 05:11.770
Intestines.

05:15.800 --> 05:16.830
Pork intestines.

05:17.270 --> 05:19.400
I was worried you wouldn't like offal.

05:19.630 --> 05:21.950
Seeing how much you enjoy it
has put my mind at ease.

05:21.950 --> 05:22.720
Don't worry.

05:22.920 --> 05:24.980
I already got all the pig feces out...

05:27.720 --> 05:28.250
I mean...

05:29.480 --> 05:31.560
I cleaned the intestines thoroughly.

05:31.560 --> 05:34.630
Mr. Zhao likes those
that have only been washed once,

05:34.920 --> 05:37.180
saying that feces give them more flavor.

05:40.430 --> 05:41.630
You scared me!

05:43.070 --> 05:43.950
What now?

05:44.360 --> 05:46.720
Do I even need to report to you
before I sneeze?

05:46.720 --> 05:47.750
But you gave me a fright!

05:47.750 --> 05:49.280
Could I have controlled it?

05:51.560 --> 05:52.690
Are you done eating?

05:53.000 --> 05:54.200
There's so much left.

05:55.680 --> 05:57.270
A few bites are already enough

05:57.270 --> 05:58.430
for me since I'm weak now.

05:58.430 --> 05:59.270
Are you sure?

05:59.630 --> 06:00.480
Yes, I'm sure.

06:01.950 --> 06:02.830
Had better not to waste it.

06:02.830 --> 06:04.040
Food is precious.

06:06.480 --> 06:07.040
Eat up.

06:13.870 --> 06:14.920
Is this...

06:15.600 --> 06:16.870
what you usually eat?

06:17.430 --> 06:19.360
We don't get to have this every day.

06:21.480 --> 06:22.560
Only when the New Year is approaching

06:22.560 --> 06:24.190
and people start butchering pigs

06:24.190 --> 06:26.390
would they give Changyu some offal.

06:27.680 --> 06:31.410
It's been a long time since I last had
noodles with pork intestines.

06:33.040 --> 06:34.500
Thank you for the noodles.

06:37.560 --> 06:39.390
A pig's tail will be served tomorrow,

06:39.390 --> 06:41.250
since Changyu will butcher a pig.

06:44.190 --> 06:46.120
-You know how to butcher pigs?
-No.

06:48.480 --> 06:50.390
How is it possible
for a delicate and sweet girl

06:50.390 --> 06:52.120
such as myself to butcher pigs?

06:52.310 --> 06:54.110
My sister was running her mouth.

06:55.510 --> 06:56.510
Don't believe it.

07:11.630 --> 07:13.390
You stay here. Keep quiet.

07:22.870 --> 07:24.130
Changning, come here.

07:24.720 --> 07:26.250
Let's play hide-and-seek.

07:29.600 --> 07:30.560
Open the door!

07:31.120 --> 07:32.150
Open up!

07:36.560 --> 07:37.870
She's a pig butcher.

08:09.390 --> 08:10.870
You were a good pig in this life.

08:10.870 --> 08:12.670
Be a good person in the next life!

08:19.920 --> 08:21.780
I'll feed you by butchering pigs!

08:32.110 --> 08:34.630
Changning, time to wash your face!

08:39.150 --> 08:39.750
Come on.

08:45.550 --> 08:48.150
Changyu, where is your silver hairpin?

08:48.960 --> 08:49.480
I pawned it.

08:49.480 --> 08:52.000
You pawned the hairpin Mom gave you?

08:52.150 --> 08:53.630
She would be upset.

08:56.480 --> 08:59.480
Don't worry.
I've struck a deal with Mr. Luo.

09:00.150 --> 09:02.960
I'll redeem the hairpin
as soon as I earn enough money.

09:02.960 --> 09:04.220
Miss Fan, are you home?

09:06.080 --> 09:06.750
Miss Fan.

09:07.670 --> 09:09.630
Chef Li told me
to collect half a pig here.

09:09.630 --> 09:10.080
Got it!

09:26.750 --> 09:28.270
Here's the pay for the pork.

09:28.270 --> 09:28.960
Thanks.

09:29.390 --> 09:30.270
Take care!

09:39.720 --> 09:42.360
Changyu, when did you butcher that pig?

09:42.670 --> 09:44.080
At the crack of dawn.

09:46.390 --> 09:47.480
Stop telling everyone

09:47.480 --> 09:48.960
that I'm a pig butcher.

09:50.030 --> 09:51.600
Changyu, did you pawn the hairpin

09:51.600 --> 09:53.600
to support that handsome young gentleman?

09:53.600 --> 09:54.150
Shh.

09:56.150 --> 09:57.390
Keep it down.

09:57.390 --> 09:59.030
Or people might hear us.

09:59.600 --> 10:01.870
I did it to save his life.

10:02.670 --> 10:04.080
Mrs. Zhao was right.

10:04.480 --> 10:06.280
The cost to support a man is high.

10:06.600 --> 10:08.800
I have to work harder to make more money.

10:09.430 --> 10:12.830
[South Market]

10:12.890 --> 10:17.430
[Meat]

10:21.310 --> 10:27.650
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

11:00.960 --> 11:02.020
You're all sweaty.

11:05.150 --> 11:06.150
Impressive, huh?

11:12.910 --> 11:14.630
Dad, Mom, I brought food.

11:18.080 --> 11:18.720
Look,

11:19.360 --> 11:21.620
you're all sweaty just like your father.

11:22.550 --> 11:23.360
Let's eat.

11:23.480 --> 11:24.210
-Sure.
-Yes.

11:24.320 --> 11:24.780
Come on.

11:27.150 --> 11:28.350
These are yours, Dad.

11:28.670 --> 11:29.320
Mom.

11:30.150 --> 11:30.910
Here you are.

11:31.720 --> 11:32.600
How is it, Dad?

11:32.600 --> 11:33.200
Very good.

11:33.720 --> 11:35.390
I really love your cooking.

11:37.910 --> 11:38.840
Changyu.

11:39.790 --> 11:42.870
Are you reopening
your family's butcher shop?

11:46.600 --> 11:47.390
Yes.

11:48.750 --> 11:50.950
I'll continue what my parents started.

11:51.170 --> 11:51.750
[Fan's Butcher Shop]
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

11:51.750 --> 11:52.750
Hello, welcome.

11:54.440 --> 11:55.550
How about this piece?

11:55.550 --> 11:56.790
It's fresh.

11:58.450 --> 11:59.150
[Boiled Dough Foods]

11:59.150 --> 12:01.120
I guarantee it's fresh.

12:01.350 --> 12:02.360
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

12:02.360 --> 12:03.240
How much is the offal?

12:03.240 --> 12:04.360
[Meat]

12:04.360 --> 12:05.270
Ma'am,

12:06.080 --> 12:08.000
offal is not sold separately today.

12:08.000 --> 12:09.910
This is the opening day of my shop.

12:09.910 --> 12:11.080
For each catty of pork you buy,

12:11.080 --> 12:12.360
I'll throw in one tael of offal.

12:12.360 --> 12:13.670
First come, first served.

12:13.670 --> 12:15.270
Really? What a bargain.

12:16.270 --> 12:18.080
I'll take... 5 catties of pork belly then.

12:18.080 --> 12:19.010
Coming right up.

12:19.390 --> 12:21.360
Pork belly is 20 maces per catty.

12:21.440 --> 12:23.630
But since you're the first customer today,

12:23.630 --> 12:25.430
I'll lower the price to 18 maces.

12:26.000 --> 12:27.960
You do know how to do business, miss.

12:27.960 --> 12:29.630
I'll buy from you again!

12:30.670 --> 12:31.400
Here you are.

12:31.630 --> 12:32.470
Take your pork.

12:32.470 --> 12:34.320
Great.

12:35.750 --> 12:37.280
And here is your free offal.

12:37.630 --> 12:38.670
Thank you so much.

12:39.720 --> 12:40.750
Here's the pay.

12:42.270 --> 12:42.960
Take it. Thanks.

12:42.960 --> 12:43.760
Do come again!

12:44.030 --> 12:45.630
I will, definitely.

12:45.630 --> 12:46.160
Alright.

12:46.270 --> 12:47.840
How much is this?

12:47.840 --> 12:49.150
The meat is very fresh.

12:49.510 --> 12:51.480
Pork belly is 20 maces per catty today.

12:51.480 --> 12:52.610
I'll take one catty.

12:52.720 --> 12:53.870
For each catty of pork you buy today,

12:53.870 --> 12:56.070
I'll throw in one tael of braised offal.

12:56.200 --> 12:57.510
You can have this for free.

12:57.510 --> 12:59.840
Changyu! Changyu!

12:59.870 --> 13:01.480
Changyu, stop selling pork this way!

13:01.480 --> 13:02.290
Mr. Guo!

13:02.760 --> 13:03.000
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

13:03.000 --> 13:04.440
One must not break the rules

13:04.440 --> 13:05.870
when doing business, right?

13:05.870 --> 13:07.150
I know this is your shop's opening day.

13:07.150 --> 13:07.440
Why do you have to offer offal for free?

13:07.440 --> 13:08.860
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

13:08.920 --> 13:09.200
[Meat]

13:09.200 --> 13:09.960
Mr. Guo,

13:10.090 --> 13:12.600
I'm only giving a special offer
on this occasion

13:12.600 --> 13:13.550
for good luck.

13:14.030 --> 13:15.560
How am I breaking the rules?

13:16.070 --> 13:18.070
You are, with what you're doing now.

13:18.480 --> 13:21.120
Is anyone else than you
giving away free offal?

13:21.320 --> 13:22.840
Enough, Guo Dali.

13:23.000 --> 13:24.550
Why bicker with a young girl?

13:24.550 --> 13:26.210
She's only selling half a pig.

13:26.270 --> 13:26.800
I'm talking to her.
How is it involving you now?

13:26.800 --> 13:28.350
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

13:28.350 --> 13:29.540
Yeah, Mr. Guo.

13:30.120 --> 13:32.000
Are you picking on me

13:32.080 --> 13:34.960
because I'm parentless
and all by my lonesome?

13:35.320 --> 13:36.360
Exactly!

13:36.600 --> 13:37.790
How can you do this?

13:37.960 --> 13:39.840
It's wrong to bully this young girl.

13:39.840 --> 13:41.100
You're way out of line!

13:42.080 --> 13:43.390
Fine, fine, fine.

13:44.030 --> 13:45.270
Today is an exception then.

13:45.270 --> 13:47.330
Don't throw in offal again tomorrow.

13:47.360 --> 13:48.270
Got it!

13:48.510 --> 13:50.970
This policy was meant to last one day
anyway.

13:51.200 --> 13:52.390
Go with it then.

13:52.840 --> 13:54.840
You're a real meddler!

13:55.750 --> 13:57.610
I need to save some for sale later.

14:00.270 --> 14:02.960
Fan's Butcher Shop has just opened!

14:03.120 --> 14:04.840
Buy pork and get free braised offal!

14:04.840 --> 14:05.960
Twenty maces per catty!

14:05.960 --> 14:07.270
Day-fresh pork!

14:07.870 --> 14:09.840
Pork belly is 20 maces per catty today.

14:09.840 --> 14:10.310
How much would you like?

14:10.310 --> 14:10.720
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

14:10.720 --> 14:11.270
I'll take one catty.

14:11.270 --> 14:11.890
One catty, right?

14:11.890 --> 14:13.090
Three catties for me!

14:13.390 --> 14:14.790
Two hundred and seventy.

14:15.550 --> 14:16.880
Two hundred and eighty.

14:17.670 --> 14:19.000
Two hundred and ninety.

14:19.120 --> 14:19.910
Changyu!

14:20.510 --> 14:20.780
Changyu!

14:20.780 --> 14:22.960
[Butcher Shop]

14:22.960 --> 14:26.360
-Mr. Zhao, listen, today, I've earned...
-You listen to me first.

14:26.360 --> 14:29.720
Your uncle brought some goons
from the gambling house to your place.

14:29.720 --> 14:32.200
They're turning your home upside down
for the title deed.

14:32.200 --> 14:32.960
What?

14:35.630 --> 14:35.720
[Butcher Shop]

14:35.720 --> 14:36.600
Filthy scum.

14:37.120 --> 14:37.790
Changyu!

14:38.150 --> 14:40.960
Why are you carrying that knife?
Don't make unwise decisions!

14:40.960 --> 14:41.320
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

14:41.320 --> 14:43.200
Oh no. She's going to kill.

14:48.550 --> 14:50.360
Song Yan, open the door!

14:50.870 --> 14:51.720
Song Yan!

14:54.030 --> 14:55.000
Song Yan!

14:56.150 --> 14:56.960
Song Yan!

14:57.320 --> 14:59.630
Song Yan,
Fan Erniu and his wife treated you well.

14:59.630 --> 15:01.960
You should come out and defend Changyu!

15:03.840 --> 15:04.750
Song Yan!

15:07.000 --> 15:09.320
Song Yan, open the door!

15:09.510 --> 15:11.200
I know you're in there!

15:11.440 --> 15:12.390
Song Yan!

15:13.390 --> 15:14.360
Song Yan!

15:14.840 --> 15:15.790
Song Yan!

15:16.320 --> 15:17.720
A life is at stake!

15:17.960 --> 15:18.910
Song Yan!

15:19.480 --> 15:20.480
Song Yan!

15:21.320 --> 15:22.080
Sit down.

15:22.750 --> 15:24.030
Focus on your studies.

15:24.840 --> 15:25.600
Mother,

15:26.480 --> 15:27.510
Changyu is in trouble.

15:27.510 --> 15:28.510
I must go help her.

15:28.840 --> 15:32.000
Fan Daniu is Fan Changyu's uncle.

15:32.390 --> 15:33.510
This is essentially

15:33.510 --> 15:35.390
an affair within the Fan family.

15:35.790 --> 15:37.870
What does it have to do
with us the Song family?

15:37.870 --> 15:40.080
How can I contribute to the country
if I can't even help a family?

15:40.080 --> 15:41.670
Why should I take the imperial exam
and strive

15:41.670 --> 15:42.750
to become an official if I just ignore

15:42.750 --> 15:44.200
an ongoing dispute near my doorsteps?

15:44.200 --> 15:45.600
Stepping out of this door

15:46.000 --> 15:49.530
is bidding farewell
to scholarly honors and official careers.

15:49.750 --> 15:50.630
Song Yan!

15:51.080 --> 15:53.480
Have you learned nothing from those books?

15:54.000 --> 15:55.390
Do you have no respect

15:55.390 --> 15:57.750
for your father's dignity and pride
at all?

15:57.750 --> 15:58.600
Son,

15:59.910 --> 16:01.510
we went to such great lengths

16:01.790 --> 16:03.960
to cancel your engagement to that jinx.

16:03.960 --> 16:06.150
If you stand up for her today,

16:06.550 --> 16:08.910
you'll give a chance
to those gossipmongers

16:08.910 --> 16:11.110
to tarnish your reputation, won't you?

16:12.480 --> 16:14.960
Mrs. Zhao, stop yelling.

16:15.670 --> 16:17.930
Song Yan is no longer engaged to Changyu.

16:18.000 --> 16:20.510
Why would he and his mother help her?

16:21.000 --> 16:22.120
Enough, Granny Kang.

16:22.120 --> 16:24.120
Changyu is pitiful
just because her parents died?

16:24.120 --> 16:26.200
My mother passed away a long time ago too.

16:26.200 --> 16:27.630
Has anyone pitied me?

16:27.630 --> 16:28.960
Stop it.

16:29.320 --> 16:30.360
Song Yan!

16:30.630 --> 16:32.320
Song Yan, open the door now!

16:32.320 --> 16:34.480
Mrs. Zhao! Mrs. Zhao!

16:35.120 --> 16:36.600
What's going on with Changning?

16:36.600 --> 16:38.440
She's been gasping for breath.

16:41.720 --> 16:42.550
Changning!

16:43.870 --> 16:44.630
Changning!

16:44.630 --> 16:46.150
Don't be afraid.

16:48.600 --> 16:49.930
Sniff it. Nice and slow.

16:50.480 --> 16:51.390
No rush.

16:53.670 --> 16:54.600
Changyu's here.

16:55.390 --> 16:56.990
She's even carrying a knife.

16:57.030 --> 16:58.760
She's not going to kill, is she?

16:59.080 --> 17:00.960
Shortly after her father's death,

17:00.960 --> 17:02.790
her uncle's already trying to seize
her and her sister's property.

17:02.790 --> 17:04.589
Even a rabbit will bite when cornered.

17:04.589 --> 17:05.400
Changning,

17:05.440 --> 17:07.040
-Are you alright?
-Changyu.

17:08.720 --> 17:09.920
Mrs. Zhuang, Mrs. Zhao,

17:09.920 --> 17:10.880
take care of Changning for me.

17:10.880 --> 17:11.589
Sure.

17:20.750 --> 17:21.829
Let's go.

17:26.310 --> 17:27.829
Let's see if we can help.

17:41.160 --> 17:42.490
Stop what you're doing!

17:43.680 --> 17:46.480
Changyu, you're finally back.

17:52.130 --> 17:54.480
[Jin Yuanbao]

17:54.480 --> 17:55.790
You're back, Miss Fan.

17:58.270 --> 17:59.200
Take your men...

18:00.270 --> 18:01.400
and get out of here.

18:03.310 --> 18:06.170
Things work by certain rules
in the gambling house.

18:06.310 --> 18:08.440
Fan Daniu claimed this house to be his,

18:08.960 --> 18:10.890
so I came to look for the title deed,

18:13.350 --> 18:15.610
with which he'll pay his gambling debts.

18:15.720 --> 18:17.650
You told them you owned this house?

18:19.880 --> 18:20.790
Changyu...

18:22.550 --> 18:25.160
I didn't have a better choice.

18:25.720 --> 18:26.880
M-M-My dear niece,

18:27.070 --> 18:28.710
please do your uncle a favor.

18:28.710 --> 18:29.270
[Fill Your Belly]

18:29.270 --> 18:31.830
Please give them the house
to pay off my debts.

18:31.850 --> 18:32.710
I promise I will

18:33.310 --> 18:35.640
treat you and Changning

18:35.640 --> 18:37.880
like my own daughters from now on.

18:37.880 --> 18:38.920
Alright?

18:40.000 --> 18:42.350
Why not give them your house instead?

18:43.480 --> 18:44.960
But where are my wife and I

18:44.960 --> 18:46.680
supposed to live that way?

18:47.070 --> 18:49.830
Changning and you will both get married
in the future.

18:49.830 --> 18:51.960
This house will be of no use to you then.

18:53.920 --> 18:56.680
What Changning and I do with
the stuff left by our parents

18:56.680 --> 18:58.080
is none of your business.

18:58.440 --> 18:59.440
Did you hear that?

18:59.590 --> 19:01.050
He doesn't own this house.

19:01.750 --> 19:04.070
I'm your uncle. I...

19:04.830 --> 19:05.430
Come here!

19:06.160 --> 19:06.760
Come here!

19:06.960 --> 19:08.550
-Mr. Jin, Mr. Jin...
-Don't move!

19:08.550 --> 19:09.160
Mr. Jin!

19:10.480 --> 19:12.740
If you don't give me the title deed today,

19:13.590 --> 19:15.030
I'll have to chop off a hand of his

19:15.030 --> 19:16.360
and show it to the brass.

19:17.550 --> 19:19.070
I'll count to three.

19:20.680 --> 19:21.400
One.

19:22.960 --> 19:23.640
Two.

19:28.680 --> 19:29.880
Use this cleaver.

19:30.510 --> 19:31.350
It's sharp.

19:31.790 --> 19:33.320
One chop's enough to cut off

19:33.680 --> 19:35.680
the skin, flesh, muscles and bones.

19:36.070 --> 19:38.400
It'll spare my uncle from some suffering.

19:40.550 --> 19:42.680
You... You...

19:43.830 --> 19:45.160
You're joking, right?

19:45.160 --> 19:46.830
You started this joke first.

19:54.550 --> 19:55.680
Fan Changyu!

19:56.200 --> 19:58.110
Your parents both died
because you're a jinx!

19:58.110 --> 20:00.760
Are you also going to have me,
your own uncle, killed now?

20:00.760 --> 20:03.590
Nobody wants you, little miss.
Even your fiancé ditched you.

20:03.590 --> 20:03.620
How dare you keep this house
as your dowry?

20:03.620 --> 20:05.280
[Fill Your Belly]

20:06.310 --> 20:07.790
Will any man put his life at risk

20:07.790 --> 20:09.350
and marry you, a jinx?

20:12.200 --> 20:13.000
You...

20:14.880 --> 20:16.480
get out of my sight right now.

20:16.590 --> 20:18.640
Otherwise, unlike them,
I won't take your hand,

20:18.640 --> 20:19.790
but your life!

20:20.200 --> 20:21.330
I'll kill you first,

20:22.030 --> 20:24.030
and then myself
as an apology to my parents!

20:24.030 --> 20:24.830
Miss Fan,

20:25.920 --> 20:28.310
we from the gambling house are
reasonable people.

20:28.310 --> 20:29.770
The Legal Code of Great Yin

20:30.070 --> 20:32.720
says that the property of a citizen
who has no male heir

20:32.720 --> 20:35.640
should be inherited by the closest kin,
such as brothers.

20:35.640 --> 20:37.590
Even if you take this matter
to the magistrate's office,

20:37.590 --> 20:40.250
this house will be awarded
to Fan Daniu the same.

20:41.350 --> 20:42.310
That's right.

20:42.920 --> 20:45.850
Those from the gambling house
are truly reasonable.

20:46.510 --> 20:48.880
Now that the Legal Code of Great Yin
also supports that I have this house,

20:48.880 --> 20:50.480
what are you lot waiting for?

20:50.720 --> 20:51.790
Continue to...

20:53.640 --> 20:55.570
look for the title deed for Mr. Jin!

20:56.710 --> 20:59.730
[Fill Your Belly]

21:01.160 --> 21:02.310
Search carefully.

21:32.110 --> 21:36.510
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

21:43.550 --> 21:44.200
Dad,

21:45.310 --> 21:47.110
if I defiantly break your rules,

21:49.440 --> 21:50.570
please don't be mad.

21:52.790 --> 21:53.640
Changning!

21:54.750 --> 21:56.350
Turn around and count to ten.

22:03.200 --> 22:04.440
One.

22:09.000 --> 22:10.220
[Fill Your Belly]

22:11.140 --> 22:12.070
[Fill Your Belly]

22:12.070 --> 22:12.960
Two.

22:18.830 --> 22:19.880
Three.

22:23.960 --> 22:24.960
Four.

22:31.920 --> 22:33.110
Five.

22:44.590 --> 22:45.830
Six.

22:53.880 --> 22:54.960
Seven.

22:59.000 --> 23:01.030
Will you go away or not?

23:01.030 --> 23:01.960
Eight.

23:02.680 --> 23:04.610
You idiots. Team up and attack her!

23:07.270 --> 23:08.270
Nine.

23:26.310 --> 23:28.440
I've only counted to nine.

23:29.920 --> 23:32.350
I might as well quit this business

23:33.590 --> 23:35.390
if I let a young girl beat me down!

23:37.550 --> 23:38.640
Watch out!

23:55.960 --> 23:59.310
You're ganging up on a parentless girl
in broad daylight!

23:59.550 --> 24:01.200
Where is your...

24:22.400 --> 24:23.000
My Lord.

24:26.680 --> 24:28.940
All the damaged items are recorded here.

24:29.400 --> 24:30.200
Pay for these,

24:30.510 --> 24:32.310
and this matter will be settled.

24:37.150 --> 24:37.990
Jin Yuanbao,

24:38.680 --> 24:40.720
you're 27 years old now, aren't you?

24:41.720 --> 24:43.640
Instead of raising a family
and pursuing a career,

24:43.640 --> 24:45.400
you're stirring up trouble all the time.

24:45.400 --> 24:47.130
Can you face your grandmother?

24:48.200 --> 24:50.310
W-We'll pay for her losses.

24:50.550 --> 24:52.510
Then who will pay for our medical bills?

24:52.510 --> 24:54.830
The four muscular men of you
were defeated by a woman.

24:54.830 --> 24:55.070
I...

24:55.070 --> 24:56.750
And you have the gall to ask her
to foot your medical bills?

24:56.750 --> 24:57.550
Get lost now.

24:58.790 --> 24:59.640
Wait!

25:02.530 --> 25:06.160
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

25:06.160 --> 25:08.820
You knocked over
my parents' memorial tablets.

25:10.790 --> 25:12.850
You can't leave until you apologize.

25:13.590 --> 25:14.350
Officer,

25:14.960 --> 25:17.270
I should be the owner of this house.

25:17.270 --> 25:18.830
If you have problems about its ownership,

25:18.830 --> 25:21.200
then write a complaint
and submit it to the magistrate's office.

25:21.200 --> 25:21.750
I...

25:22.590 --> 25:24.030
For damaging these memorial tablets,

25:24.030 --> 25:25.350
you'll be flogged 20 times

25:25.350 --> 25:26.750
if she decides to sue you.

25:32.150 --> 25:32.960
Mr. Fan Erniu,

25:32.960 --> 25:33.880
Ms. Meng Lihua,

25:34.270 --> 25:35.000
we're sorry.

25:35.110 --> 25:35.790
We're sorry.

25:35.790 --> 25:36.850
Please forgive us.

25:37.260 --> 25:38.050
We apologize!

25:38.050 --> 25:38.440
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

25:38.440 --> 25:39.310
We apologize!

25:39.590 --> 25:40.440
We apologize.

25:47.510 --> 25:49.040
I'll leave this money here.

25:54.030 --> 25:54.830
You may go now.

26:00.030 --> 26:01.960
Come on. A word in private.

26:02.070 --> 26:03.750
-Go!
-Mr. Jin, Mr. Jin...

26:03.790 --> 26:04.290
Mr. Jin.

26:04.350 --> 26:04.830
Mr. Jin!

26:10.640 --> 26:11.680
Keep this safe for your sister.

26:11.680 --> 26:12.680
I knew it was right

26:13.030 --> 26:14.510
to ask you to come over.

26:15.550 --> 26:17.410
Though Fan Erniu is gone forever,

26:17.440 --> 26:19.400
your friendship with him remains.

26:19.510 --> 26:21.400
But I'm afraid Fan Daniu won't stop

26:21.400 --> 26:22.800
fighting for this house.

26:25.310 --> 26:26.160
Changyu.

26:30.110 --> 26:30.960
Changyu!

26:33.030 --> 26:36.160
A young girl has to sustain
an entire household alone...

26:37.030 --> 26:38.510
How unfortunate.

26:39.620 --> 26:42.030
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]

26:42.030 --> 26:42.720
Dad,

26:43.920 --> 26:46.120
you told me to never let anyone see me use

26:46.410 --> 26:46.640
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

26:46.640 --> 26:48.510
the long-handled blade techniques
you taught me

26:48.510 --> 26:50.640
except in the face of imminent danger.

26:51.790 --> 26:53.650
But I disobeyed your order today.

26:54.270 --> 26:56.350
I beg for your forgiveness, Dad, Mom.

26:59.590 --> 27:01.720
I'm sure your father will forgive you.

27:05.270 --> 27:06.730
You're severely injured.

27:06.750 --> 27:07.920
Why did you come out

27:08.110 --> 27:09.640
instead of resting inside?

27:10.000 --> 27:11.400
There was too much noise.

27:11.590 --> 27:13.390
I thought I'd come out for a look.

27:19.260 --> 27:21.800
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

27:22.550 --> 27:23.750
"Fan Erniu..."

27:26.640 --> 27:28.700
So your father was not only a butcher,

27:29.880 --> 27:31.740
but also a martial practitioner.

27:33.000 --> 27:34.110
You heard all that?

27:38.110 --> 27:40.040
Before my father became a butcher,

27:40.350 --> 27:41.950
he worked as an armed escort.

27:43.160 --> 27:45.020
Your mother was named Meng Lihua.

27:46.680 --> 27:47.940
Was that her real name?

27:50.310 --> 27:51.840
Yes. My mother was amazing.

27:53.110 --> 27:54.310
She was literate.

27:56.310 --> 27:57.770
She composed fragrances.

27:58.880 --> 27:59.940
The other butchers

28:00.350 --> 28:01.510
and their homes reek

28:02.480 --> 28:04.010
when pigs are slaughtered.

28:04.400 --> 28:05.930
But my home is an exception.

28:06.480 --> 28:08.310
All our washed clothes would be scented

28:08.310 --> 28:10.310
with the incense made by my mother

28:12.310 --> 28:13.770
to purge all the bad odors.

28:14.270 --> 28:14.880
Folks,

28:15.070 --> 28:15.880
there's nothing to see here.

28:15.880 --> 28:17.000
Stop watching, folks.

28:17.000 --> 28:17.750
Dismissed!

28:17.750 --> 28:19.160
-Leave!
-Go home!

28:20.400 --> 28:21.270
Thank you.

28:21.720 --> 28:23.850
Today, those people were in the wrong.

28:25.830 --> 28:27.310
But they did make a point.

28:27.720 --> 28:29.850
If Fan Daniu really files a complaint,

28:30.270 --> 28:32.350
Changyu will probably lose her house.

28:32.350 --> 28:33.880
Is there anything we can do?

28:33.960 --> 28:36.350
Changyu and her sister
are all by themselves.

28:36.350 --> 28:38.000
You must help them.

28:38.270 --> 28:39.870
I didn't say I wouldn't help.

28:45.640 --> 28:47.300
There is actually a solution.

28:49.310 --> 28:50.000
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

28:50.000 --> 28:52.350
How did your parents pass away?

28:53.440 --> 28:54.510
They met bandits.

28:55.200 --> 28:56.800
My father's throat was slit.

28:57.510 --> 28:58.590
He died on the spot.

28:59.440 --> 29:02.970
My mother was drawing her last breath
when she was brought home.

29:05.110 --> 29:07.570
She hung in there
for six to eight whole hours

29:09.270 --> 29:11.310
just to speak to me and my sister.

29:15.070 --> 29:17.400
But she didn't manage to say
a single word.

29:23.070 --> 29:26.130
All she could do was give me the hairpin
she was holding.

29:29.160 --> 29:31.490
Your parents definitely won't blame you.

29:35.070 --> 29:37.130
This gauze isn't stained with blood.

29:37.270 --> 29:37.960
It's clean.

29:41.480 --> 29:42.270
Thanks.

29:43.160 --> 29:44.220
Unlike me, at least

29:44.790 --> 29:47.190
your parents were with you
when you grew up.

29:49.590 --> 29:51.480
At least you still have your sister,

29:51.480 --> 29:52.920
your own flesh and blood.

29:54.310 --> 29:55.200
At least...

29:55.480 --> 29:58.160
you still have your home
where you've lived for many years.

29:58.160 --> 29:59.550
By contrast, my parents

30:01.070 --> 30:02.600
were gone when I was little.

30:05.550 --> 30:07.350
How did they pass away?

30:16.750 --> 30:17.950
War took their lives.

30:26.200 --> 30:29.270
Well, as parentless children,

30:30.590 --> 30:32.850
we shouldn't be comparing our miseries.

30:34.200 --> 30:35.030
Sorry.

30:35.640 --> 30:37.640
I reminded you of your painful past.

30:40.550 --> 30:42.410
You've figured out the truth now.

30:43.510 --> 30:45.790
I'm just a butcher with brute strength.

30:46.510 --> 30:47.750
Laugh if you want.

30:51.680 --> 30:53.140
You not only saved my life,

30:54.160 --> 30:55.790
but also have been trying to raise money

30:55.790 --> 30:56.790
to provide for me.

30:57.640 --> 30:58.790
Wouldn't it make me an ingrate

30:58.790 --> 31:00.200
to laugh at you?

31:05.480 --> 31:08.510
Changyu! Changyu!

31:08.680 --> 31:10.590
Mrs. Zhao wants to see you.

31:11.110 --> 31:12.570
Don't tell anyone I cried.

31:14.550 --> 31:15.080
Let's go.

31:16.510 --> 31:17.160
Careful.

31:19.880 --> 31:21.480
Will he get well?

31:21.480 --> 31:22.510
Will he fully recover?

31:22.510 --> 31:25.960
At worst, there might be
lingering issues in his legs.

31:26.160 --> 31:26.960
His other body parts will be fine.

31:26.960 --> 31:28.090
Mr. Zhao, Mrs. Zhao!

31:28.720 --> 31:30.050
There you are, Changyu.

31:30.480 --> 31:31.440
Come on in.

31:32.640 --> 31:34.900
We'd like to discuss something with you.

31:37.200 --> 31:38.640
Look at the snow on your head.

31:38.640 --> 31:39.830
What's the matter?

31:40.310 --> 31:41.370
Why so mysterious?

31:59.110 --> 32:00.880
Mrs. Zhao, just speak your mind.

32:00.880 --> 32:02.280
I'll do whatever you say.

32:08.550 --> 32:10.080
Have a matrilocal husband?

32:12.510 --> 32:14.830
It's Constable Wang's idea.

32:14.830 --> 32:15.750
Best advice ever.

32:15.750 --> 32:17.000
Look, this way,

32:17.070 --> 32:19.110
there will be a male heir to your father,

32:19.110 --> 32:20.640
and you can keep your house.

32:20.680 --> 32:22.720
Fan Daniu won't be able to snatch it away.

32:22.720 --> 32:24.000
This house is all

32:24.110 --> 32:26.200
your parents left for you and your sister.

32:26.200 --> 32:27.640
If it's gone,

32:28.000 --> 32:29.550
how are you supposed to live?

32:29.550 --> 32:31.920
Yeah. Parents usually choose husbands

32:32.070 --> 32:34.350
carefully for their daughters.

32:35.200 --> 32:36.720
Changyu really lives a bitter life.

32:36.720 --> 32:39.270
What decent young man would agree
to be a matrilocal husband?

32:39.270 --> 32:41.070
Extreme conditions call for
extreme solutions, right?

32:41.070 --> 32:42.480
Changyu has to find a matrilocal husband

32:42.480 --> 32:44.160
if she is to keep her house.

32:44.550 --> 32:46.200
What's a matrilocal husband?

32:46.200 --> 32:47.920
That refers to...

32:47.920 --> 32:49.400
a man who your sister

32:49.400 --> 32:51.000
will spend the rest of her life with,

32:51.000 --> 32:52.930
and who can take care of you and her.

32:53.680 --> 32:55.640
Then I want that handsome young gentleman
to be this man.

32:55.640 --> 32:56.590
Not him!

32:57.270 --> 32:58.270
Why not?

32:58.790 --> 33:01.680
Based on my ten-odd years
of matchmaking experience,

33:01.680 --> 33:03.410
I can tell he's a decent fellow.

33:04.270 --> 33:05.800
Mrs. Zhao, as you just said,

33:06.110 --> 33:08.440
what decent young fellow would agree
to be a matrilocal husband?

33:08.440 --> 33:10.830
My wife has been a matchmaker
for over a decade.

33:10.830 --> 33:13.200
She's seen more young men
than you've seen pigs.

33:13.200 --> 33:15.530
You should take her expert advice on this.

33:16.030 --> 33:18.720
Besides,
Chongzhou is an active combat zone now.

33:18.720 --> 33:20.480
I heard the military would launch
a recruitment again.

33:20.480 --> 33:23.030
Every family's hurrying
to arrange marriages now,

33:23.030 --> 33:24.760
just to ensure they have heirs.

33:24.880 --> 33:26.070
Finding a matrilocal husband

33:26.070 --> 33:28.110
is even harder than reaching the heavens!

33:28.110 --> 33:28.920
Yan Zheng can't be my husband.

33:28.920 --> 33:29.830
Why can't he?

33:29.830 --> 33:30.790
He just can't!

33:30.790 --> 33:31.550
But why?

33:31.880 --> 33:32.430
He...

33:32.430 --> 33:33.750
Alright. Keep it down.

33:35.350 --> 33:36.590
Yan Zheng

33:37.030 --> 33:38.830
is badly injured

33:39.720 --> 33:42.790
and will probably have trouble
with his legs after he recovers.

33:42.790 --> 33:45.000
He even doesn't have identity papers
or travel permits.

33:45.000 --> 33:45.880
Nonetheless,

33:46.830 --> 33:47.920
the silver lining

33:48.200 --> 33:50.350
is that he's a choice within your reach!

33:50.350 --> 33:50.960
Right?

33:51.030 --> 33:53.590
Changyu, this is a win-win opportunity

33:53.590 --> 33:54.720
for both of you.

33:54.960 --> 33:56.550
Neither of you are taking advantage
of each other.

33:56.550 --> 33:58.010
-But...
-My wife's right.

33:58.110 --> 33:59.920
You just promised to do

33:59.920 --> 34:00.750
whatever I say.

34:00.750 --> 34:01.680
Mrs. Zhao...

34:01.680 --> 34:02.480
Knock it off!

34:02.920 --> 34:03.790
Mr. Zhao.

34:04.920 --> 34:08.050
I know you both want what's the best
for Changning and me.

34:08.190 --> 34:10.550
But please let me mull it over.

34:11.710 --> 34:13.320
What is there to think about?

34:13.920 --> 34:15.110
-Changyu.
-Changyu!

34:15.110 --> 34:16.310
-Changyu!
-Changyu!

34:23.150 --> 34:24.400
Why are you sighing?

34:34.320 --> 34:35.280
Changyu,

34:36.030 --> 34:37.280
tell me what you think

34:37.800 --> 34:39.400
is wrong with that lad.

34:44.150 --> 34:44.949
Do you mean...

34:45.280 --> 34:46.610
he can't perform in bed?

34:48.440 --> 34:49.030
Don't worry.

34:49.030 --> 34:50.030
I'll ask my husband

34:50.030 --> 34:51.360
if there's a cure.

34:51.510 --> 34:53.110
That's not what I mean.

34:53.550 --> 34:55.080
Don't read too much into it.

34:56.280 --> 34:58.540
What if Yan Zheng rejects this proposal?

34:59.510 --> 35:01.840
You're a beautiful young lady
who can provide for the family

35:01.840 --> 35:03.150
by butchering pigs.

35:03.510 --> 35:04.910
Who is he to turn you down?

35:05.400 --> 35:07.960
Besides, he doesn't have identity papers
or travel permits.

35:07.960 --> 35:08.800
If he marries you,

35:08.800 --> 35:10.150
at least he won't be taken for a refugee

35:10.150 --> 35:12.000
and sent to the Vanguard Battalion.

35:12.000 --> 35:14.150
How can I force him
to be a matrilocal husband

35:14.150 --> 35:15.410
after I just saved him?

35:16.480 --> 35:18.540
It's blackmail through owed favors.

35:20.360 --> 35:22.320
His opinion aside,

35:23.110 --> 35:24.320
he'll inevitably

35:26.800 --> 35:28.860
become the same as Song Yan over time.

35:32.150 --> 35:34.880
Scholars always betray
those who love them.

35:35.480 --> 35:37.630
But Yan Zheng is not a scholar.

35:38.030 --> 35:40.290
He's nothing like that ingrate Song Yan.

35:44.800 --> 35:45.590
Mrs. Zhao,

35:46.920 --> 35:48.280
Yan Zheng...

35:49.510 --> 35:51.190
is like a piece of tallow white jade

35:51.190 --> 35:53.400
that I stumbled upon in the snow—

35:54.360 --> 35:55.110
beautiful,

35:56.030 --> 35:56.670
lustrous,

35:57.400 --> 35:58.280
and valuable.

35:59.320 --> 36:01.050
But I don't own this jade piece,

36:01.630 --> 36:03.510
not even if it's carved

36:03.510 --> 36:04.630
with my name on it.

36:05.150 --> 36:07.510
Then put your name on it
and keep it for yourself for now.

36:07.510 --> 36:08.710
If anyone comes looking for it,

36:08.710 --> 36:10.190
we'll return it.

36:12.510 --> 36:13.920
Yan Zheng already said

36:14.880 --> 36:16.710
that he'd leave upon recovery.

36:18.000 --> 36:20.630
When he has a wonderful girl like you
as his wife

36:20.630 --> 36:21.710
and leads a stable life here,

36:21.710 --> 36:23.000
will he ever want to leave?

36:23.000 --> 36:25.880
He'll probably stick around
even if you tell him to go!

36:25.880 --> 36:27.480
My dearest Mrs. Zhao,

36:27.920 --> 36:31.070
it's not a good idea to coerce him
into marrying a butcher.

36:31.070 --> 36:32.670
Forced fruit is never sweet.

36:33.360 --> 36:35.840
It doesn't matter,
as long as it quenches your thirst.

36:35.840 --> 36:37.320
If Yan Zheng dares to say no,

36:37.320 --> 36:38.550
I'll toss him out!

36:38.800 --> 36:40.360
If you had saved a donkey,

36:40.360 --> 36:41.670
it'd pull the millstone for you.

36:41.670 --> 36:42.590
I'll talk to him if you don't.

36:42.590 --> 36:43.150
Don't!

36:48.590 --> 36:49.920
I'll talk to him myself.

37:09.760 --> 37:10.690
Is something up?

37:12.150 --> 37:13.080
Come in and talk.

37:25.320 --> 37:25.840
I...

37:27.960 --> 37:29.030
I'm wondering...

37:33.920 --> 37:36.030
I'm wondering if I can do laundry for you!

37:36.030 --> 37:36.960
But those are...

37:37.110 --> 37:38.040
You're welcome!

37:41.960 --> 37:43.360
Those are clean clothes.

37:52.110 --> 37:54.040
Where did these clothes come from?

37:54.280 --> 37:55.280
I snatched them.

37:56.360 --> 37:57.630
I'm going to wash them.

37:58.840 --> 38:00.040
Let me help, Changyu.

38:21.400 --> 38:22.130
Here you are.

38:31.550 --> 38:32.670
Yan Zheng...

38:35.710 --> 38:37.030
Would you be my...

38:38.320 --> 38:39.520
matrilocal husband?

38:41.280 --> 38:43.320
When I recover and leave,

38:43.320 --> 38:44.480
I'll pay you money.

38:46.880 --> 38:47.800
But I don't want money.

38:47.800 --> 38:48.880
I want you.

38:49.760 --> 38:50.510
If you refuse,

38:50.510 --> 38:51.440
I'll beat you up!

38:55.360 --> 38:56.820
Then you'd better kill me.

38:57.070 --> 38:59.800
Or you'll have to pay extra
to get me medical help.

39:00.670 --> 39:01.360
You...

39:02.000 --> 39:03.400
Don't squeal, piggy.

39:04.110 --> 39:04.920
Be serious.

39:06.110 --> 39:07.960
You're now acting as Yan Zheng.

39:08.510 --> 39:09.320
Focus.

39:14.150 --> 39:16.550
Uncle didn't get the title deed yesterday.

39:17.550 --> 39:18.750
He'll probably lodge

39:20.550 --> 39:22.950
a complaint with the magistrate's office.

39:23.630 --> 39:25.280
To keep this house,

39:26.190 --> 39:27.400
my only option

39:29.190 --> 39:30.990
is to find a matrilocal husband.

39:35.280 --> 39:36.410
Mom and Dad are dead.

39:40.030 --> 39:42.160
This house is the only thing they left.

39:43.630 --> 39:45.890
I can't lose it.
It's not only for my sake,

39:47.840 --> 39:49.570
but also for Changning's sake.

39:53.320 --> 39:55.980
I'm not forcing you
to marry into the Fan family.

39:56.110 --> 39:57.280
I'm just...

40:00.360 --> 40:01.280
asking.

40:14.630 --> 40:17.030
Dry weather!

40:18.000 --> 40:20.710
Beware of fire!

40:21.510 --> 40:22.400
Come in.

40:28.440 --> 40:30.070
Mr. Zhao and Mrs. Zhao are both asleep.

40:30.070 --> 40:32.270
I was worried no one would serve you tea.

40:36.360 --> 40:37.550
You'd easily get chilly
after losing blood.

40:37.550 --> 40:38.320
That tea has turned cold.

40:38.320 --> 40:39.320
Don't drink it.

40:39.880 --> 40:41.010
I made you some soup.

40:42.030 --> 40:43.030
Thank you.

40:54.280 --> 40:55.070
This is...

40:55.960 --> 40:58.360
Pork liver soup. It helps replenish blood.

41:01.550 --> 41:04.190
One bucket of offal
was left from yesterday,

41:04.590 --> 41:06.450
so I made this soup for you with it.

41:12.320 --> 41:13.150
It's a bit hot.

41:13.800 --> 41:14.840
I'll eat it later.

41:19.670 --> 41:21.630
You hate offal, don't you?

41:23.550 --> 41:25.610
You had only a few bites of the noodles

41:25.760 --> 41:27.620
with pork intestines yesterday.

41:27.880 --> 41:30.410
You also dislike this pork liver soup,
right?

41:35.280 --> 41:36.810
I wouldn't say I dislike it.

41:37.360 --> 41:38.710
I'm just...

41:39.840 --> 41:40.640
not used to it.

41:44.110 --> 41:45.190
But...

41:46.190 --> 41:48.320
I'm not able to offer anything better.

41:50.320 --> 41:52.000
Pork liver soup helps replenish blood.

41:52.000 --> 41:53.460
It's good for your health.

41:53.940 --> 41:56.880
Just pretend it's medicine and eat it.

42:01.480 --> 42:02.610
I'll leave you to it.

42:06.360 --> 42:07.150
Miss Fan.

42:17.360 --> 42:18.420
I'll do as you said.

42:20.280 --> 42:21.740
Then eat it while it's hot.

42:22.400 --> 42:23.510
No, I mean...

42:25.110 --> 42:26.320
I agree to be...

42:27.030 --> 42:28.490
your matrilocal husband.

42:49.960 --> 42:50.590
Great.

42:56.670 --> 42:57.840
If you stay,

43:00.190 --> 43:01.280
I'll feed you by butchering pigs.
